extendedInfo.description: The street food revolution has given rise to North America's tastiest, juiciest fleet of mobile eateries and Eat St. wants to be your fearless captain.The new Eat St. Android app, developed by Invoke and Paperny Entertainment, can now direct you to the best street food dishes and food trucks in your city, as verified by the experts â street food aficionados like you. The Eat St. App will display local delicacies and the carts that serve them. The interactive map makes finding your next street meal a breeze. You can even watch clips of Eat St. featured carts directly on your phone! Open wide and sink your teeth into this brand new Eat St. App for Android. For more information about the Eat St. App or TV Series, visit http://eatst.foodnetwork.ca/

reviews.title: Good in Seattle
reviews.comment: Works in Seattle/Tacoma area. I\'ve always loved late night street food.   Possible improvement: Menu Photos: ask food truck owners to post a photo of their written menus to view....saw this in the Houston area for locating trucks and was a great help.
reviews.author: Kit Frymier

reviews.title: Terrible app
